---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="Frequently Asked Questions - Opal Design">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <HeroSection 
      title="Frequently Asked Questions"
      highlightText="Questions"
      description="Welcome to the cozy corner of clarity! If you're curious, cautious, or just a little lost in the moonlight — I’m here to help. Below are some of the most commonly whispered wonders from our visitors." />
    
    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="space-y-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 slide-up">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">✨ Who exactly is behind Opal Design?</h3>
            <p>Opal Design is a cozy creative studio led by a magical feline (that’s me!) and a very real human who believes in gentle transformation, thoughtful tools, and designing life from the inside out. Whether you're here for soulful resources, quiet magic, or custom support — you’re in kind paws.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 slide-up" style="animation-delay:100ms">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">🛍 What kind of products or services do you offer?</h3>
            <p>We offer a mix of cozy digital tools, charming guides, and softly powerful services. These might include:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
              <li>✒️ Personalized scripts for hard conversations</li>
              <li>📒 Life design templates & planners</li>
              <li>🔮 Crystals for your cozy home</li>
              <li>🐱 Special support from Opal herself — in the form of chats or guided prompts.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-2">We also take on custom requests when the stars align.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 slide-up" style="animation-delay:200ms">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">📨 I sent a message — who responds?</h3>
            <p>Opal receives all messages with a swish of her tail, but depending on the topic, either she or her human counterpart will reply. Don’t worry — everything is read with care, and no fluff is skipped.</p>
          </div>
           <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 slide-up" style="animation-delay:300ms">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">🧾 Do you accept custom requests?</h3>
            <p>Yes! We love cozy, curious ideas. Whether it’s a tailored template, a magical collaboration, or something uniquely you — just let us know on the contact page. We’ll see if the stars align.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 slide-up" style="animation-delay:400ms">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">🕊 Is this a shop or a blog or… what exactly?</h3>
            <p>It’s a little bit of both. Think of Opal Design as a living library with magical corners: part resource hub, part product haven, part quiet support space. It’s not just a store — it’s a sanctuary for designing a softer, more intentional life.</p>
          </div>
          
           <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 slide-up" style="animation-delay:500ms">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">💌 Will I get emails from you if I message you?</h3>
            <p>Only if it’s about your request! We won’t send newsletters unless you specifically subscribe. Opal respects your inbox like a sunbeam: only welcome when invited.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 slide-up" style="animation-delay:600ms">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">🔒 How do you handle privacy?</h3>
            <p>Gently and securely. We don’t sell or share your information — ever. Your messages are for our eyes (and paws) only. This space is sacred and safe.</p>
          </div>
          
           <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 slide-up" style="animation-delay:700ms">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">🕰 How quickly will I hear back?</h3>
            <p>Usually within 1–3 business days, unless Opal is taking a moon nap. If your message is urgent or time-sensitive, be sure to mention that — we’ll do our best to respond swiftly.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 slide-up" style="animation-delay:800ms">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">🌙 Can I just say hi without buying anything?</h3>
            <p>Oh, please do! Cozy visits and kind words are always welcome here. This isn’t just about transactions — it’s about connection.</p>
          </div>
          
            <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 slide-up" style="animation-delay:900ms">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">💭 What if I have a question not listed here?</h3>
            <p>Meow! That means you’re curious — and we love that. Pop over to the contact page and ask away. We'll respond with whiskered wisdom soon.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

